 test","Update Debian/systemd docs","Fix references to pre-56 Troubleshooting admin menu","Drill through no longer works for pivot tables in the latest version","Fix flaky test for metabase-browser custom element","Card filters seem to be avoiding the linkage to dashboard filters","Discard cached field values will... refresh the values?","Fix tabs alignment for horizontal tabs with grow (#61895)","docs: translations limitations","skip flaky loki row chart tests","There are more selected columns than there are total columns","refactor(sdk): Rename embedding-sdk directory to embedding-sdk-bundle","chore: upgrade vulnerable cipher-base package","chore: upgrade vulnerable sha.js package","[BOT-316] Metabase BE support for dynamic agent profiles","Respond with HTTP status 500 when Store API request fails during Cloud migration","fix(sdk): Add background-light to derived colors for the new embed","Content Translation doesn't translate pivot table columns","publicly-shared dashboards show blank pages when viewed in incognito (or by non-authenticated users)","[Metabot] Add `available_actions` to metabot context","Download button overlaps table header with embedding title is not enabled.","Cannot assign certain column types to fields in models","[QP] Don't apply `:coercion-strategy` to joined fields twice","feat(embed js flow): use widget for initial parameters","Fix invitation not being sent from /setup flow","Data picker skeleton is vertically shifted","[Search] Increase search reporting","Content translation copy uses wrong header name","[METABOT] Do not apply update-keys to ai-service request state","Cast to a Datetime doesn't play well with Joins on the Query Editor","Labels on inputs in the new-dashboard modal are incorrectly using font-weight: 800","dashboardId must be an int - error displayed for embedded maps with more than 1000 pins","bump arrow to 17 for parquet issue","Edit visualization on visualizer cards in dashboard view mode does not save the changes","Autos